tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE music_sales_data (
    sale_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    sale_date DATE,
    album_name VARCHAR(255),
    artist_name VARCHAR(255),
    genre VARCHAR(50),
    sales_quantity INT,
    sale_amount DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE music_sales (
  sale_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  date DATE,
  artist_name VARCHAR(50),
  album_name VARCHAR(50),
  units_sold INT
);

CREATE TABLE music_sales (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    album_title TEXT,
    artist TEXT,
    sale_date DATE,
    units_sold INT
);

CREATE TABLE sales_regions (
    region_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    region_name TEXT,
    country TEXT,
    city TEXT,
    postal_code TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE sales_trends (
    trend_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    trend_name TEXT,
    trend_description TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE music_sales (
  sale_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  song_name VARCHAR,
  artist_name VARCHAR,
  sale_date DATE,
  sale_amount DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE albums (
  album_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  album_name VARCHAR,
  release_date DATE,
  artist_id INT,
  genre VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE sales_reports (
  report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  report_date DATE,
  total_sales DECIMAL,
  most_sold_genre VARCHAR,
  top_artist VARCHAR
);
